List resources from a MainCurrent or class_character object

Source: R/S7_method_resources.R
list_resources.Rd

List resources from a MainCurrent or class_character object

Usage

list_resources(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An object of class MainCurrent or class_character

...

Additional arguments?

Value

A list of API resources

Examples

MainCurrent("enrollees") |> list_resources()
